Revision history for Text-Transliterator

1.04 13.06.2023
  - better presentation for Unaccenter->char_map_descr()
  - move pod tests to xt/

1.03 08.07.2017
  - fixes in Build.PL and Git repository structure (no functionality changes)

1.02 12.05.2016
  - fixed wrong underscore in source text (\xA0 instead of \x5f) ...
    it went unnoticed until perl v5.25.1 !

1.01 10.02.2013
  - using tr[..][..] instead of tr/../../, in case '/' would be in the input
  - localization of $@ before eval
  - same $VERSION for both modules
  - META.yml links to source repository

1.00 13.07.2012    
  - Initial release

